  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I told her, after work, come right away to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I made her she has to wash herself, not to neglect, because I had water.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I save for her, if I could, a potato or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And a little warmer was in my-- in the-- in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so she didn't survive, and that's all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I said there came a few.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- and they-- they-- they were hungry there too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because it was a shortage of food for the German too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Maybe not for the real in Berlin, they had it that good.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But in the other places.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But she wasn't the worst.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because she could be worse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They-- they did the right thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She could with me, they could give me a-- give me a bullet in the head.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And finally, came the time when the Russian approached.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a doctor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because later comes out it was different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not yet my end--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--of the career.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So here I have-- I was the doctor, [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I ?] [? was ?] [? today. ?] And she trusted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She didn't check with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I made the little-- so somebody wasn't so sick, I kept her a day, whole.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is called [INAUDIBLE] amenorrhea, from the shock, and I myself too, right?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- they said they poisoned-- they gave something in the food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was only six or seven days in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the seventh-- this is emotional.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is called [INAUDIBLE] amenorrhea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I want to say that the girls told me that in the factory, there are some-- there were some people who gave them a piece of bread and gave them an apple sometimes.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
